 Jose TMy wife and I were involved in a really bad auto collision. Of course it was Lloyd Baker who handled this case. Our vehicle was a total loss which caused us numerous injuries. We are extremely satisfied on how the case was handled and the final result. Long story short... our first Experience with this law firm was around 10 years ago. Relocating from Santa Barbara area in California to Las Vegas was not easy, but once the family was settled here I convinced my mother to move out here as well. Unfortunately a short time after she did, she was involved in a horrific car accident. Mother was T-boned at an intersection and she was severely injured.
It was a difficult time for the whole family and important decisions had to be made, like hiring a good and trustworthy attorney to handle the serious case. It was definitely a difficult decision due to the numerous Attorney advertisements. We called a few and visited a couple but we could not agree on one. We finally ended up in Mr. Lloyd Baker's office. After that first meeting we knew and agreed that he would be the attorney to handle mother's case. It was the best decision we made. The recovery was slow but successful and thorough the entire process they were there, 100%. We never felt like there was questions or doubts that they didn't have the answers to. Now in days, especially here in Las Vegas, TRUST is an extremely important matter. As a family man, Minister and local business owner, I am very careful where I put my word, but when it comes to these matters I do not hesitate for a second to Trust and recommend Lloyd Baker Law to Family and Friends.
Thank you Lloyd and all the Firm for exceeding our expectations.
Ooh, and as far as Mother's settlement... Let's just say, they took care of business.
Martin OI used Mr. Baker to help me with 2 car accident cases and a dispute with a business. I was very pleased with the helpful and professional way he took care of my situations. The outcome was very positive, I could tell he and his staff worked hard to make sure things were resolved in a timely manner.  He went above and beyond what I was expecting. I would recommend his services to anyone for experienced professional legal help.
