Yolanda CI was referred to Lloyd Baker's office through a friend of mine after being injured in an auto accident. I was very pleased with the knowledge, attentiveness to my case and care that Lloyd Baker's staff provided me with during this process. I recommend anyone in need of a personal injury attorney to call Mr. Baker's office for a consult.
Brian RAt first i was just looking for some advice, but Lloyd Baker and his team assured me that I do have a case. His office will work with you on everything and you will be informed every step of the way. I hope I don't ever need his services ever again, as I do not want to ever be in any legal trouble, but if I do ever need an attorney again, Lloyd Baker is who I am calling!!
Vhari MWe were involved in two car accidents one month apart from each other. Both my husband and I were injured in both accidents and our cars were totaled. Our case was a complicated one, but Lloyd Baker and his team made everything so much easier and got us the compensation we deserved. They dealt with the insurance companies who were so difficult and so rude and caused us so many sleepless nights before our awesome attorney got involved. I highly recommend this office and I'm so pleased with the work they did for us.
Andie SGreat service! I've had other cases at other firms and this attorney's office was by far my best experience. The staff is knowledgeable, respectful, and they answer and return my calls. Do yourself a favor and use Lloyd Baker Attorneys for your personal injury case.
D. LivingstonI'm so thankful for Lloyd Baker and his team! I was referred to Lloyd's office several years ago to assist me with a traffic citation I received. The service his firm provided was free and they appeared in court on my behalf and my citation was reduced to a parking ticket. I was relieved! Unfortunately, last year I was involved in a motor vehicle accident. I didn't know what to do, but I remembered how his team helped me with my citation and I didn't think twice about calling him first after I started getting the run around from the insurance company.
During the process of treatment you become a little disconnected and set back. Lloyd's team is very professional, honest, compassionate and patient. My calls were always answered or returned right away, never rushed and I received excellent advice! Lloyd personally reached out to me on several occasions to see how I was doing. He reassured me that his team was doing everything possible to help me and he really wanted me to focus on getting better. I just wanted to say Thank you to all of you for your hard work and for finalizing my claim quickly! I'd feel very confident in referring your law firm to my family and friends!
Steve GI have been represented by Lloyd and his team for over two years following a head on collision. I would hate to be on the opposing end of his team. They are relentless and tenacious in their approach to anyone who attempts to hold back from their clients. I hope I never need Lloyd's services again or have to go through the pain, but if I or anyone I know is involved in an accident, Lloyd Baker Attorneys will be my first call.
 








